00:01:15.140 --> 00:01:19.180
This was hugely important--it changed people’s
way of looking at themselves and the world,

00:01:19.180 --> 00:01:23.880
it led to wider European literacy, and eventually
forced governments to grant religious freedoms,

00:01:23.880 --> 00:01:28.280
while also at the same time maybe being more
of a political revolution than a religious one.

00:01:28.280 --> 00:01:30.439
So, during the European Middle Ages, the Catholic

00:01:30.439 --> 00:01:36.560
Church really dominated European civilization.
It’s almost impossible to imagine the scope

00:01:36.560 --> 00:01:39.640
