their confessions, providing last rites.

00:01:56.049 --> 00:02:01.880
The church also provided all of the social services:
It distributed alms to the poor, and ran orphanages,

00:02:01.880 --> 00:02:06.420
and provided what education was available.
And most Europeans would in their lives meet

00:02:06.420 --> 00:02:11.590
exactly one person who could read the Bible,
which was only available in Latin - their

00:02:11.590 --> 00:02:16.099
parish priest.
And, the church owned over 1/3 of all the

00:02:16.099 --> 00:02:20.459
land in Europe, which helped make it the most
powerful economic and political force on the

00:02:20.460 --> 00:02:24.740
continent. And the Pope claimed authority
over all the kings of Europe, as the successor

00:02:24.750 --> 00:02:28.750
